Legault-Dubois offers a wide range of inspection (prepurchase, maintenance, etc), expertise services (water infiltration, mold, ice dam, odors, basement issues, attic issues) and lab analysis (mold, asbestos, vermiculite, water, radon) for home, condos and commercial buildings.
